1 WHEREAS, William "Billy" Henry D'Aquilla is survived by his sons, Sam D'Aquilla
2 and Andy D'Aquilla (Kelly); daughter, Mary Dreher (Kevin); grandsons, Nicholas D'Aquilla
3 (Megan), Will D'Aquilla, Collin D'Aquilla, and Drew D'Aquilla; granddaughters, Sara
4 D'Aquilla, Maria D'Aquilla, Josie D'Aquilla, and Annie Robinson; great-granddaughter,
5 Abigail D'Aquilla; great-grandsons, Henry D'Aquilla and Ari Robinson; and brother,
6 Michael D'Aquilla (Jackie); he will be deeply missed, but the legacy of his love, generosity,
7 and service to the St. Francisville community shall live on in perpetuity in the hearts and
8 minds of those who were privileged to have known and loved him.
9 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
10 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby express heartfelt condolences on the death of William
11 "Billy" Henry D'Aquilla and does hereby extend sincere wishes that his family, friends, and
12 loved ones find comfort in their shared memories of his beautiful life.
